package au.edu.anu.rscs.aot.queries.graph.node

Queries applying to Nodes and TreeNodes .

Author:
Jacques Gignoux - 4 oct. 2021
  • Class Summary
    Class
    Description
    HasEdges
    Check if a Node has Edges that satisfy some constraints like a Query, a class Id, a multiplicity.
    HasParent
    Check if a TreeNode has a parent that satisfies an (optional) query.
    IsNode
    Check if a Node is the same as the one passed to the constructor.
    IsOneOf
    Check if a Node is found in the list of nodes passed to the constructor.
    NodeCharacteristics
    Check if a Node is a leaf or root node.
    NodeEdges
    A Query to select Edges linked to a Node.
    NodeListEdges
    A Queryable to select In, OUT or all edges of a list of Nodes.
    TreeQuery
    Get parts of a Tree starting from a TreeNode.
